00:00:07.290 --> 00:00:09.950
But we'll try it out.

00:00:09.950 --> 00:00:12.430
I'm going to ask you to pick
a number between 1 and 30.

00:00:12.430 --> 00:00:14.270
Don't say it out loud,
but pick a number

00:00:14.270 --> 00:00:15.930
between 1 and 30.

00:00:15.930 --> 00:00:17.290
Have you done that?

00:00:17.290 --> 00:00:18.190
