00:00:38.070 --> 00:00:40.000
Say pass, something like that.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.210
OK, so let me know.

00:00:41.210 --> 00:00:42.060
BRADY HARAN: Yes

00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:44.660
JAMES GRIME: Yes.

00:00:44.660 --> 00:00:45.420
Do you see your number?

00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:46.270
BRADY HARAN: No.

00:00:46.270 --> 00:00:47.950
JAMES GRIME: No.

00:00:47.950 --> 00:00:49.280
Do you see your number?

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:50.330
BRADY HARAN: No.

00:00:50.330 --> 00:00:51.800
JAMES GRIME: No?

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:53.920
Do you see your number?

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:54.810
BRADY HARAN: No.

00:00:54.810 --> 00:00:55.255
JAMES GRIME: No.

00:00:55.255 --> 00:00:56.910
Do you see your number?

00:00:56.910 --> 00:00:57.830
BRADY HARAN: Yes.

00:00:57.830 --> 00:00:58.880
JAMES GRIME: Yes.

